cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.IR 

This paper deals with computer vision-based methods and deep learning classifiers for detection of railway track defects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses transfer learning, which is a popular technique in machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) the second most likely category. The paper also involves the use of artificial intelligence (AI) for automation, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a likely category. The paper also discusses the monitoring of the rail network, which involves robotics and control (cs.RO) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques.
